name: JPNDC Brewery Complex
directions: Upstairs on “First” floor (above ground floor), accessible via elevator as long as Mike’s Fitness is open. From main entrance, elevator is on the right next to Bella Luna takeout door/counter. Take elevator to floor 1, head left down long hallway with ramp, then up a short flight of stairs or via the lift, turn left down hallway before Keshet office and then right at end of hall. Restrooms are on the left next to dance studio, one designated “women’s” with two stalls but/and an external locking door, and one designated gender neutral with both stall & urinal.
comment: Open to anyone using the brewery complex/the public. If after business hours, doors to stairwell may be locked, but elevator is open for as long as the gym is open.
